title: What Does Amazon's BSR mean? || Amazon BSR
description:
Are you new to Merch By Amazon? Are you tired of low sale numbers? 

Then this video is for you!! In this video I explain what AMAZON's BSR means and how you can use it to improve your sales on your E-Commerce business on Amazon. Using the tips shown in this video you can grow your merch by amazon account and rise quickly up those tier levels.
